  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: Deep cut across the stomach from a scimitar, bleeding uncontrollably.\n\nStory:
    Mustafa, a deserter from the Ottoman lines, presses trembling fingers to his
    spilling entrails. He prays in Turkish under his breath, not knowing if God listens
    to a traitor. His eyes search yours in desperation \u2014 if neither side remembers
    him, was there ever a man called Mustafa at all?\n\n\nRequired bandages to heal:
    3"
